      * L11: 001100 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
      * L12: 001200     ACCEPT X.
      * L13: 001300     ACCEPT Y.
      * L14: 001400     IF (X > Y)
      * L15: 001500         MOVE Y TO N1
      * L16: 001600         MOVE X TO N2
      * L17: 001700     ELSE
